sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Developer or reviewer
    participant App as Product app
    participant Workbench as SDD Workbench
    participant API as Bridge backend
    participant Files as Current workspace SDD files
    participant Diagram as Diagram Viewer
    participant Feedback as Feedback Queue
    participant Codex as Codex Workflow

    User->>App: Open with CODEX_BRIDGE_DEV_MODE=true
    App->>Workbench: Open current-project SDD panel
    Workbench->>API: GET /sdd/project?workspace_path=current
    API->>Files: Read specs, tasks, and diagrams
    Files-->>API: Read-only SDD snapshot
    API-->>Workbench: Project SDD data
    User->>Workbench: Open project diagram
    Workbench->>Diagram: Render .mmd source
    User->>Diagram: Mark node, edge, or region
    Diagram->>Feedback: Create feedback with diagram metadata
    User->>Workbench: Request Codex update
    Workbench->>Codex: Send workspace, SDD path, and selection context
    Codex->>Files: Propose diagram/spec/task update
    Files-->>Workbench: Updated SDD snapshot
